  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  dBP 90-109mmHg due to pre-existing or gestational hypertension; live fetus(es); and
             20-33+6 weeks.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  dBP consistently &lt; 85mmHg by home BP monitoring; severe systolic hypertension;
             proteinuria; contraindication to either arm of the trial or to prolongation of
             pregnancy; or known lethal/major fetal anomaly.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
